ranythingllm

Anything LLM is The all-in-one Desktop & Docker AI application with full RAG and AI Agent capabilities. ranythingllm is a R interface of Anything LLM API.

Installation

Install the developing version from Github.

devtools::install_github('byzheng/ranythingllm')
